:$b + 1/(x+$a) 
x < -$a \bigvee x > -$a
\mathbb{R} 
x < $a \bigvee x > $a
x < 0 \bigvee x > 0
y < $b \bigvee y > $b
y < -$a \bigvee y > -$a
\mathbb{R} 
y > $a

:$b + 1/(x-$a)
x < $a \bigvee x > $a
\mathbb{R} 
